fected** - Response times increased by 16.8x, suggesting potential issues with the underlying TiDB database.\n\n2. **Redis performance degradation** - Both HMSET and HGET operations show 9.6x latency increases, indicating Redis infrastructure problems.\n\n3. **Cascading effects** - The Redis and ProductCatalogService issues are propagating upstream to CartService and CheckoutService.\n\n4. **Multiple frontend instances affected** - All three frontend instances (frontend-0, frontend-1, frontend-2) show similar patterns of increased latency when calling downstream services.\n\nThe root cause appears to be infrastructure-related, potentially affecting both the database layer (TiDB for ProductCatalogService) and cache layer (Redis for CartService).", "metric_analysis_findings": "基于收集到的监控指标数据，我已经完成了对故障期间的全面扫描分析。以下是详细的异常发现：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"region_pending\", \"pod_cpu_usage\", \"rrt_max\", \"rrt\", \"node_memory_usage_rate\", \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\", \"node_cpu_usage_rate\", \"pod_processes\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"tidb-tikv\",\n      \"reason\": \"TiDB集群出现region_pending异常飙升，从正常中位数11018增加到故障期间1085，变化率164.14%，同时p99值也从20351.52增加到1890.76，变化率166%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"region_pending指标显著异常：正常中位数11018.0，故障中位数1085.0，变化率164.14%；p99值从20351.52增加到1890.76，变化率166%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis-cart-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Pod资源使用异常，pod_cpu_usage从正常中位数0.0变为故障期间0.0，但p99值从0.11变为0.0，变化率200%，同时pod_processes保持稳定\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_cpu_usage p99值从0.11变为0.0，变化率200%；pod_processes保持1.0不变\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"服务响应时间异常，rrt_max从正常8222.5下降到故障期间5704.0，变化率36.17%，p99值从83983.46下降到33322.72，变化率86.37%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max中位数从8222.5下降到5704.0，变化率36.17%；p99值从83983.46下降到33322.72，变化率86.37%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-03\",\n      \"reason\": \"节点内存使用率异常，node_memory_usage_rate从正常28.56%下降到